\f0\fs28 \cf2 Form field errors will use in-line validation according to the following method:\ \ When a user gives focus to a field and stops typing for 1 second, the field will validate. Depending on the success of the entry, either a or a will be shown.\ \ If there is an error and the user pauses typing for at least 2 seconds, blurs the field, or hovers over the corresponding a message will pop up describing the nature of the issue.\ \ Once a user gives focus to a field with an error and begins typing, the error will disappear (fade out) and validation will reoccur as normal.}
